{"tid":11470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（2016年11月下旬末）東北季候風為本港帶來清涼天氣","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T23:54:49.000Z","uid":38255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8235ec9bbf94ee94311ec32a7c8fc141aadc43","tid":11470,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"￼&nbsp;氣象討論：2016年11月下旬&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n此帖文討論期：2016年11月21日至30日&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n高登氣象台專頁現已登場&nbsp;<br />\n￼<a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather%C2%A0&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b580df47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather&nbsp;</a><br />\n￼<a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather%C2%A0&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=486be124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather&nbsp;</a><br />\n﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n◤溫度術語&nbsp;<br />\n嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C&nbsp;<br />\n﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n◤參考網頁&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6e806103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2d41ece0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=df747715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ec885ef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n◆ 香港天文台電腦預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fnhm%2Fnhm_uc.htm&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2d6865e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=49f84f9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈<br />\n<br />\n赤的疑惑<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n21/11/2016 0:52<br />\n<br />\n高登氣象台專頁正式登場&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我們自2008年起在香港高登討論區發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵&nbsp;<br />\n￼<a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather%C2%A0&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b580df47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather&nbsp;</a><br />\n￼<a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather%C2%A0&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=486be124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather&nbsp;</a><br />\n￼<a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ddde13fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a>"},{"pid":"b3ea94630f85dd70b8e1712a648b0f028a9ee5c6","tid":11470,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"赤巴馬sir等等大人物未揸定主意，<br />\n我lead住先直至有大人物接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW高登AC bam左，淨copy到字，<br />\ncopy唔到代碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7243e24e23f2e78da3f277153884864bc4405f11","tid":11470,"uid":27881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08306e822d1feb7bae0c53c9d83a3a9d9da2cfa6","tid":11470,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae8e2aac8cc473da23c21bda940652446b4bc52","tid":11470,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10: